AARON HASKINS, 342 acs.
Henrico Co. on Beaver Pond Br.;
adj. Benjamin Cheatham, James
Gates, Moseley, & William Gates;
15 Mar 1744/45, p.233. £1.S15.

JAMES HUNT, 104 acs. Surry Co.
on the S side of Nottoway Riv.;
adj. his own lines, Clements
Handcock & Mr Thomas Eldridge;
20 Sep 1745, p.487. 10 Shill.

SAMUEL VAUGHAN, 317 acs.
Pr. Geo. Co. on the lower side of
George’s Br. of Nammiseen Cr.;
adj. Eppes, Boiseau, Stell, Mayes,
Tatum, Wells, Griffin & Vaughan;
20 Sep 1745, p.534. £1.S15.

WILLIAM HARDING, 240 acs.
Henrico Co. crossing the Main
Road, in a Slash & a small Br.;
adj. John Ealom, Philip Jones, Seth
More, Dawson, & James Cashoon;
20 Sep 1745, p.540. £1.85.
